metadata.name: TeraCube: The Last Human: Kansas
metadata.description:
"Fuck it, we are all ash in the end." Thelonius Dankaugh, 2035.

Thelonius, the last man standing in Kansas, walks towards the cube and resigns himself to his fate. The Dimitrian strip him of his flesh and use it to create new, twisted, life forms. Out of respect to his resistance, they use his DNA for the finest of their creations. 


#generative #psychadelic #aliens #abstract
